markup.__html: Free flowing expression is always incredibly inspiring to me. The lost amusement park, @lunaluna, was created out of complete unbridled creativity and play from the most prominent artists of the 20th century. Lost for over 30 years, it’s now being displayed in Los Angeles for the first time since 1987 thanks to @champagnepapi 🎡 🎠 Massive inspo from this experience. A must see if you get the chance ✨🎨
